                                             Section: Common IDS/IPS Methods
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

          | Signature-Based – Pattern matching against known attack signatures.
Methods   | Anomaly-Based – Statistical analysis to detect unusual behavior patterns.
